    sensed time-series. ISPRS Journal of Photogrammetry and Remote Sensing,
    98, 106-118. 
    [doi:10.1016/j.isprsjprs.2014.10.001](https://doi.org/10.1016/j.isprsjprs.2014.10.001)
  |||,
  
